text: Floralba Krasniqi (born 26 August 1994) is an Albanian football midfielder who currently plays for Union Kleinmünchen in the ÖFB-Frauenliga. ==References== Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Albanian emigrants to Austria Category:Kosovan emigrants to Austria Category:Austrian people of Albanian descent Category:Austrian people of Kosovan descent Category:Albania women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Albanian women's footballers Category:ÖFB-Frauenliga players Category:Union Kleinmünchen players
